task.summary:
Add mailing system and update project to Java 17
Introduced an email service with support for SMTP using Jakarta Mail API and an email template builder. Added a `MailServiceProvider`, `Mailable` base class, and `VerificationMail` for email workflows. Updated project dependencies and configurations for Java 17 compatibility.

Add user signup, email verification, and dashboard features
Implemented user signup flow with email verification using a unique token sent via email. Introduced a dashboard for authenticated users and improved navigation links in the login and signup pages. Updated entity relationships, added new DAO methods, and improved logging for better debugging.
